&lt;h1 id="new-year-new-blog"&gt;New year, new blog&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Feb 16 2008&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I wasn&amp;rsquo;t posting enough on my old blog since:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;SquareSpace is annoying&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;I was writing long, infrequent posts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;ll post more frequently on my new WordPress blog – shorter, more wide-ranging topics, and more as notes to self than anything else.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>新年，新博客</title><link>https://linguista.cn/naval/zh/new-year-new-blog.zh/</link><pubDate>Sat, 16 Feb 2008 16:55:29 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/naval/zh/new-year-new-blog.zh/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/naval/orig/new-year-new-blog/"&gt;原文(English)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
